THE AI ILLUSION (AND THE SHIELD YOU NEED)

AI can draft. AI can summarize. AI can sound convincing.

But AI does not understand:

- Your procedural posture
- Local rules
- What has been preserved

AI can help you write.

It cannot protect your position.

AI SHIELD PRINCIPLE:

- Builder → drafts
- Inspector → challenges
- Architect → organizes
- Strategist (you) → decides

SAFETY PROTOCOL

- Chats are not privileged
- Do not upload protected material to the cloud
- Verify all outputs
- Human decisions are final

THE SHIFT

Legal literacy: I know my rights.

Procedural literacy: I know how to protect them.

If it’s not preserved, it doesn’t exist.

BOTTOM LINE

LCES teaches how not to lose before you begin.